@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
title Sequence - Google Login

actor "Người dùng" as User
boundary "TrangĐăngNhập" as UI
control "GoogleIdentity" as Google
control "XácThựcController" as Controller
control "XácThựcService" as Service
entity "NgườiDùng" as UserModel
database "MongoDB" as DB

User -> UI : Bấm Google Login
UI -> Google : yêu cầu credential
Google --> UI : credential
UI -> Controller : POST /api/xacthuc/dang-nhap-google
Controller -> Service : xác minh credential
Service -> Google : verify id token
Google --> Service : email, name, picture
Service -> UserModel : tìm/tạo người dùng
UserModel -> DB : upsert by email
DB --> UserModel : user
UserModel --> Service : user
Service -> Service : tạo JWT
Service --> Controller : phiên đăng nhập
Controller --> UI : 200 + token
UI --> User : Vào dashboard
@enduml

